Comment: Allows the use of (dictionaries, hashmap ...) which are quite rarely used in Clash of Code.
Quick statement but gives all necessary information in a consistent way

Goal section
* Suggest to change "the Americans" to "some team members".

* Please fix "<<yd>" as "<<yd>>".

* Please state the rounding requirement.

* It is not clear that the displacements should be added together, and the reason for adding them (are they in a relay race or what?). Please add some explanation.

Input section
* Line 1: Please mention "space-separated".

* Please change "start_y" to "starty" for consistency.

* Please change "n_dir" to "ndir" for consistency.

* Please mention that the displacements are floats.

Thanks.
My goodness, you are sharp as well as active (I see your comments under many other contributions) - thanks a lot! I have updated the contribution according to your suggestions.
